<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-11-09T15:46:02-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-11-09T15:46:02-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-09T15:46:02-05:00</updated><title>英特尔高管表示 Arrow Lake 的发布“没有按计划进行”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;深蓝色背景上浅蓝色英特尔徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JEbLF4zz4_B4yHm6Wn-EzLsI7ZA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73711656/acastro_180529_1777_intel_00 01.0.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;9qa18H&quot;>;对英特尔全新基于 Arrow Lake 的 Core Ultra 9 200S 系列处理器的评论一直乏善可陈，特别是当它谈到游戏性能，但英特尔表示这还不是故事的结局。 Intel的副总裁和客户AI和技术营销的GM Robert Hallock表示，其新芯片的性能应该更好，并且该公司将尽快将其带到那里。 youtube.com/live/P2OHRH7221w?t=637s&quot;>;对 &lt;em>;HotHardware&lt;/em>; 的 Dave Altavilla 和 Marco Chiappetta 的新采访&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5Q2OxD&quot;>;英特尔&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/10/24265928/intel-core-ultra-200s-series-specs-release-date-pricing&quot;>;预先说&lt;/a >; 这些新芯片在游戏方面无法击败 AMD 芯片。但审稿人的调查结果却出乎意料地糟糕。尽管取得了一些效率提升，如 Tom Warren 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/10/24265928/intel-core-ultra-200s-series-specs-release-date-pricing &quot;>;&lt;em>;边缘&lt;/em>;对 Core Ultra 9 285K 的评测&lt;/a>;，这款新芯片似乎甚至落后于英特尔......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2024/11/9/24292221/intel-acknowledged-arrow-lake-performance-issues-robert-hallock-exec&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/9/24292221/intel-acknowledged-arrow-lake-performance-issues-robert-hallock-exec" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/9/24292221/intel-acknowledged-arrow-lake-performance-issues-robert-hallock-exec</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-09T11:49:47-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-09T11:49:47-05:00</updated><title> iOS 18 新安全功能让警方更难解锁 iPhone</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手机的照片拼贴，屏幕上有密码锁和钥匙孔。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IPGT0jTq9iOwcI09zE8iinSQ82Y=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73711323/STK478_writing_into_phone_C.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;8kR4K1&quot;>;iOS 18 有一个明显新的安全功能，可以重新启动几天没有解锁的 iPhone，这让警方更难闯入，从而让警方感到沮丧嫌疑人的 iPhone，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.404media.co/apple-quietly-introduced-iphone-reboot-code-which-is-locking-out-cops/&quot;>;根据 404 Media 报道&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;sBTY8J&quot;>;&lt;em>;404 Media，&lt;/em>;首先&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.404media.co/police-freak-out-at-iphones-mysteriously -rebooting-themselves-locking-cops-out/&quot;>;报告了警方关于周四重新启动的警告&lt;/a>;，写道，重新启动的 iPhone 会进入更安全的“首次解锁之前”或 BFU 状态。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021 的创始人克里斯·韦德 (Chris Wade) 表示，现在，苹果似乎在 iOS 18.1 中添加了“不活动重启”代码，该代码会触发 iPhone 在锁定四天后重新启动。 /8/11/22620014/apple-corellium-security-virtual-iphone-dmca-lawsuit-settled&quot;>;移动分析公司 Corellium&lt;/a>; 告诉媒体。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;KcwTaS&quot;>;代码显示在下面的屏幕截图中 &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/naehrdine/status/1854896392797360484&quot;>;由 Dr.-Ing 发布。 Jiska Classen&lt;/a>;，Hasso Plattner 研究所研究组组长。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;4gT36L&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot; data-dnt=&quot;true&quot;align=&quot;center&quot;>; &lt; p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;Apple 确实添加了一项功能...&lt;/p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2024/11/9/24292092/ios-18-security-inactivity-reboot-police-complain-unlocking-iphone-difficult&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/9/24292092/ios-18-security-inactivity-reboot-police-complain-unlocking-iphone-difficult" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/9/24292092/ios-18-security-inactivity-reboot-police-complain-unlocking-iphone-difficult</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-09T11:22:22-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-09T11:22:22-05:00</updated><title>希捷 2TB Xbox 扩展卡已恢复至迄今为止最优惠价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;连接到 Xbox Series X 的 1TB Seagate 存储扩展卡的特写图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/sGOHyKHOhCdMJIJFYSEmgi7OWx0=/0x0:996x664/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73711264/Seagate_Storage_Expansion_Card_Xbox_Press_Image.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;希捷的专有存储解决方案并不便宜，但它仍然是为您的 Series / X 配备额外空间的最简单方法。&lt;/em>; |图片：Seagate&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;aanrxW&quot;>;黑色星期五还要过几周才能到来，但亚马逊、百思买和其他零售商的假日促销活动已开始成形。我们预计，当许多早期销售&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21569881/black-friday-deals-start-time-hours-cyber-monday时，许多游戏商品将出现大幅折扣-stores&quot;>;下周开始&lt;/a>;，但如果你想提前购买，&lt;strong>;希捷适用于 Xbox Series X / S 的 2TB 存储扩展卡&lt;/strong>;&lt;em>;&lt;strong>;&lt;/ strong>;&lt;/em>;已达到历史最低价 199.99 美元（折扣 160 美元），价格为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09BJYXMDW/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.link/7x46p0sfha73r&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .seagate.com/products/gaming-drives/xbox-gaming/storage-expansion-for-xbox-series-x/&quot;>;希捷在线店面&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float- left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;XuYmDV&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;最好的立即购买 Xbox 控制器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23025443/best-xbox-controllers-one-series-xs&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;: